snippet.title: Weights & Biases
snippet.description:
Weights and Biases builds developer tools for machine learning our tool helps with experiment tracking, model optimization, and dataset versioning. Our channel features tutorials on machine learning and deep learning, how to's and demo's of our app, our podcast Gradient Dissent - conversations with industry experts, and researchers presenting their latest works. 

We’re always free for academics and open source projects.
